{"tid":518853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【車廂有蟲自炒案中案】黑警夫婦炒車涉頂包  被控妨礙司法公正","createTime":"2018-01-03T18:17:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-03T19:54:48.000Z","uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d85945616dfd132e817b3aca48e3262cefa322a0","tid":518853,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T18:17:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180103/large/1514987841_fd6e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180103%2Flarge%2F1514987841_fd6e.jpg&h=fb3753d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃大仙龍翔道去年中一宗自炒車禍，竟揭發「案中有案」，一名休班黑警涉嫌找妻子頂包。黑警經進一步調查及徵詢法律意見後，昨日(1月2日)拘捕案中姓張黑警(36歲)，控以一項妨礙司法公正及一項不小心駕駛；其37歲姓李妻子則於事發翌日被捕，亦同被控以一項妨礙司法公正，案件將於下周二(1月9日)於觀塘裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n案發於去年7月25日，一輛掛P牌的福士白色私家車，在黃大仙龍翔道失控撞石壆凌空反墮路面，警員到場發現司機不知所終，其後上門調查時，李女自稱是肇事司機，指因車廂有昆蟲受驚肇禍。惟《蘋果》爆相爆片接獲讀者提供的車Cam片，拍攝到明明是男司機，與警方資料大有出入(相關新聞︰<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2uYvCxr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2uYvCxr&d=pLCesClYAPxr%2FfDWnLqOdCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=af006b7c\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2uYvCxr</a>)。<br />\n<br />\n黑警強調，黑警非常重視人員的操守<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，任何人員干犯違法行為，黑警絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f325d24f0cc9c457f5ab083a5ebdcefbbe19649f","tid":518853,"uid":35522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T18:47:44.000Z","msg":"休班警得一分<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f6348667d8005c11b720b30e86c9f999443fbfe","tid":518853,"uid":39013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T19:19:56.000Z","msg":"屌你老母如果唔係比有心人影到又比黑警過骨<br />\n正一畜牲"},{"pid":"13c7fe6c420b6548d74c7d3d270978a8eb4a4cae","tid":518853,"uid":118827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T19:54:48.000Z","msg":"真係垃撚圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}